 <a href=\"mailto:press.office@cnc.pnn.police.uk\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"govuk-link\">press.office@cnc.pnn.police.uk</a>. Please tell us what format you need. It will help us if you say what assistive technology you use.\n\n  </div>\n</details>\n</div></section>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a7dca35e5274a5eb14e7324/FINAL_Strategy_and_Business_Plan_2014-17__PUBLIC_VERSION_.pdf\">\n        <svg class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--pdf\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 99 140\">\n  <path d=\"M12,59h9v9h-9v-9ZM30,77v9h39v-9H30ZM30,104h57v-9H30v9ZM30,122h48v-9H30v9ZM12,86h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,122h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,104h9v-9h-9v9ZM30,68h57v-9H30v9ZM35.2,21c-.3-.2-.6-.4-1-.5s-.8-.2-1.3-.2h-2.6v5.5h2.6c.5,0,1,0,1.3-.2s.7-.3,1-.5c.3-.2.5-.5.7-.8s.2-.7.2-1.1h0c0-.5,0-.9-.2-1.2-.2-.3-.4-.6-.7-.8h0ZM52.4,21.9c-.4-.5-1-.9-1.6-1.1-.7-.3-1.5-.4-2.4-.4h-2.7v11.5h2.7c.9,0,1.7-.1,2.4-.4s1.2-.7,1.6-1.1c.4-.5.7-1.1.9-1.7.2-.7.3-1.4.3-2.1v-.7c0-.8,0-1.5-.3-2.1-.2-.6-.5-1.2-.9-1.7h0ZM87,12v27H12V12h75ZM39.8,23c0-.9-.1-1.6-.4-2.4-.3-.7-.7-1.4-1.2-1.9-.5-.5-1.2-1-1.9-1.2-.8-.3-1.6-.5-2.5-.5h-7.2v17.9h3.6v-6h3.2c.9,0,1.8-.1,2.6-.5.8-.3,1.4-.7,2-1.2.5-.5,1-1.2,1.3-1.9.3-.7.5-1.5.5-2.4h0ZM57.4,26c0-1.3-.2-2.6-.5-3.7s-.9-2-1.6-2.8c-.7-.8-1.6-1.4-2.7-1.8-1.1-.4-2.3-.6-3.8-.6h-6.6v17.9h6.6c1.5,0,2.7-.2,3.8-.6,1.1-.4,2-1,2.7-1.8.7-.8,1.3-1.7,1.6-2.8.4-1.1.5-2.3.5-3.7h0ZM72.4,17.1h-12.1v17.9h3.6v-7.5h7.8v-3.3h-7.8v-3.8h8.4s0-3.3,0-3.3Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__details\">\n    <h2 class=\"gem-c-attachment__title\">\n      <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a7dca35e5274a5eb14e7324/FINAL_Strategy_and_Business_Plan_2014-17__PUBLIC_VERSION_.pdf\">Yr Awdurdod Heddlu Niwclear Sifil Strategaeth a Chynllun Busnes 2014/17</a>\n</h2>\n\n\n      <p class=\"gem-c-attachment__metadata\"><span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">484 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">11 pages</span></p>\n\n\n\n\n      <p class=\"gem-c-attachment__metadata\">This file may not be suitable for users of assistive technology.</p>\n      <details data-module=\"ga4-event-tracker\" data-ga4-event='{\"event_name\":\"select_content\",\"type\":\"detail\",\"text\":\"Request an accessible format.\",\"section\":\"Request an accessible format.\",\"index_section\":1}' class=\"gem-c-details govuk-details govuk-!-margin-bottom-0\" title=\"Request an accessible format.\">\n  <summary class=\"govuk-details__summary\">\n    <span class=\"govuk-details__summary-text\" data-ga4-expandable>\n      Request an accessible format.\n    </span>\n</summary>  <div class=\"govuk-details__text\">\n    \n        If you use assistive technology (such as a screen reader) and need a version of this document in a more accessible format, please email <a href=\"mailto:press.office@cnc.pnn.police.uk\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"govuk-link\">press.office@cnc.pnn.police.uk</a>. Please tell us what format you need. It will help us if you say what assistive technology you use.\n\n  </div>\n</details>\n</div></section>\n\n<p>There are additional materials available in Welsh. These materials include translations of previous Civil Nuclear Constabulary Police Authority (<abbr title=\"Civil Nuclear Constabulary Police Authority\">CNCPA</abbr>) Annual Reports &amp; Accounts and Strategic Plans as well as general information sheets. Please contact the Civil Nuclear Constabulary for electronic copies or further enquiries regarding our Welsh Language Scheme on 01235 466 606 or see the contact us section on our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/civil-nuclear-constabulary\" class=\"govuk-link\">homepage</a>.</p>\n\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
